<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Lista de Espera — HEKSEL GENESIS</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0a0a0a;
    --surface: #111111;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    --text: #f0efe8;
    --muted: rgba(240,239,232,0.45);
    --danger: #E24B4A;
    --success: #1D9E75;
    --radius: 12px;
    --radius-sm: 8px;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  .waitlist { width: 100%; max-width: 460px; }

  .wl-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .wl-heading {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 38px);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .wl-sub {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .wl-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .wl-stat {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
  }

  .wl-stat-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .wl-stat-value {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .wl-stat-value.bump {
    transform: scale(1.15);
    color: #1D9E75;
  }

  .wl-progress-wrap { margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }

  .wl-progress-bar {
    height: 3px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 999px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .wl-progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--text);
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: width 0.6s ease;
  }

  .wl-progress-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .wl-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .wl-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }

  .wl-input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-family: inherit;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .wl-input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }
  .wl-input:focus { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }
  .wl-input.error { border-color: var(--danger); }

  .wl-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 13px;
    background: var(--text);
    color: var(--bg);
    border: none;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: inherit;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.15s, transform 0.1s;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .wl-btn:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
  .wl-btn:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
  .wl-btn:disabled { opacity: 0.35; cursor: default; }

  .wl-success {
    display: none;
    padding: 1rem 0 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .wl-success-icon {
    font-size: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--success);
  }

  .wl-success-title {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .wl-success-pos {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .wl-success-redirect {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--success);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .wl-share { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); text-align: center; }

  .wl-share-link {
    color: var(--text);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .wl-heading { font-size: 28px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="waitlist" aria-label="Lista de espera Heksel Genesis">

  <p class="wl-eyebrow">Drop 01 — Edição limitada</p>
  <h1 class="wl-heading">Lista de espera</h1>
  <p class="wl-sub">Garanta seu acesso antecipado ao lançamento da Heksel Genesis antes que as vagas se esgotem.</p>

  <div class="wl-stats">
    <div class="wl-stat">
      <p class="wl-stat-label">Na fila agora</p>
      <p class="wl-stat-value" id="queue-count">—</p>
    </div>
    <div class="wl-stat">
      <p class="wl-stat-label">Vagas restantes</p>
      <p class="wl-stat-value" id="slots-left">—</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="wl-progress-wrap">
    <div class="wl-progress-bar">
      <div class="wl-progress-fill" id="progress-fill" style="width: 0%"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="wl-progress-meta">
      <span>Capacidade da lista</span>
      <span id="progress-pct">—</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="wl-divider" />

  <div id="form-area">
    <div class="wl-form">
      <input class="wl-input" type="text"  id="inp-name"  placeholder="Seu nome"            autocomplete="name" />
      <input class="wl-input" type="email" id="inp-email" placeholder="Seu e-mail"           autocomplete="email" />
      <input class="wl-input" type="tel"   id="inp-phone" placeholder="WhatsApp (opcional)"  autocomplete="tel" />
      <button class="wl-btn" id="submit-btn" onclick="handleSubmit()">Garantir meu acesso</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="wl-success" id="success-area">
    <div class="wl-success-icon">✓</div>
    <p class="wl-success-title">Você está na fila!</p>
    <p class="wl-success-pos" id="position-text">Sua posição: —</p>
    <p class="wl-success-redirect">Entrando no grupo VIP em <span id="redirect-count">3</span>s...</p>
    <p class="wl-share">Não redirecionou?
      <a class="wl-share-link" href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/G5q3H5MuJSyCmdAOEcf78T?s=sh&p=a&mlu=2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">clique aqui</a>
    </p>
  </div>

</section>

<script>
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//  CONTADOR REAL — usa Supabase (gratuito) para persistir entre todos os
//  visitantes. Siga o README no final do arquivo para configurar em 3 minutos.
//
//  Se ainda não configurou o Supabase, o sistema cai para localStorage
//  (funciona só por dispositivo, mas não zera enquanto o usuário não limpar
//  o cache).
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  var TOTAL_SLOTS = 3000;
  var WA_URL = 'https://chat.whatsapp.com/G5q3H5MuJSyCmdAOEcf78T?s=sh&p=a&mlu=2';

  // ── Supabase config — substitua pelos seus valores ───────────────────────
  var SUPABASE_URL = '';        // ex: 'https://xyzxyz.supabase.co'
  var SUPABASE_ANON_KEY = '';   // ex: 'eyJhbGci...'
  var SUPABASE_TABLE = 'waitlist';
  // ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

  var useSupabase = SUPABASE_URL !== '' && SUPABASE_ANON_KEY !== '';

  // ── Fallback localStorage ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
  var LS_KEY = 'heksel_waitlist_count';

  function lsGetCount() {
    var v = parseInt(localStorage.getItem(LS_KEY), 10);
    return isNaN(v) ? 0 : v;
  }

  function lsIncrement() {
    var n = lsGetCount() + 1;
    localStorage.setItem(LS_KEY, n);
    return n;
  }

  // ── Supabase helpers ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  function sbHeaders() {
    return {
      'Content-Type': 'application/json',
      'apikey': SUPABASE_ANON_KEY,
      'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
    };
  }

  function sbFetch(path, opts) {
    return fetch(SUPABASE_URL + '/rest/v1/' + path, Object.assign({ headers: sbHeaders() }, opts));
  }

  async function getCount() {
    if (!useSupabase) return lsGetCount();
    try {
      var res = await sbFetch(SUPABASE_TABLE + '?select=id', {
        headers: Object.assign(sbHeaders(), { 'Prefer': 'count=exact', 'Range': '0-0' })
      });
      var total = res.headers.get('content-range');  // ex: "0-0/42"
      if (total) return parseInt(total.split('/')[1], 10) || 0;
      return 0;
    } catch(e) { return lsGetCount(); }
  }

  async function insertEntry(name, email, phone) {
    if (!useSupabase) return lsIncrement();
    try {
      await sbFetch(SUPABASE_TABLE, {
        method: 'POST',
        body: JSON.stringify({ name: name, email: email, phone: phone || null })
      });
      return await getCount();
    } catch(e) { return lsIncrement(); }
  }

  // ── UI ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  function fmt(n) { return n.toLocaleString('pt-BR'); }

  function updateStats(count) {
    var slots = Math.max(0, TOTAL_SLOTS - count);
    var pct   = Math.min(100, Math.round((count / TOTAL_SLOTS) * 100));

    document.getElementById('queue-count').textContent = fmt(count);
    document.getElementById('slots-left').textContent  = fmt(slots);
    document.getElementById('progress-pct').textContent = pct + '%';
    document.getElementById('progress-fill').style.width = pct + '%';

    return count;
  }

  function bumpCounter() {
    var el = document.getElementById('queue-count');
    el.classList.add('bump');
    setTimeout(function() { el.classList.remove('bump'); }, 400);
  }

  // ── Submit ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  async function handleSubmit() {
    var nameEl  = document.getElementById('inp-name');
    var emailEl = document.getElementById('inp-email');
    var phoneEl = document.getElementById('inp-phone');
    var name    = nameEl.value.trim();
    var email   = emailEl.value.trim();
    var phone   = phoneEl.value.trim();

    nameEl.classList.remove('error');
    emailEl.classList.remove('error');

    var valid = true;
    if (!name)  { nameEl.classList.add('error');  valid = false; }
    if (!email || !email.includes('@') || !email.includes('.')) {
      emailEl.classList.add('error'); valid = false;
    }
    if (!valid) return;

    var btn = document.getElementById('submit-btn');
    btn.disabled = true;
    btn.textContent = 'Aguarde...';

    // Salva e busca contagem atualizada
    var newCount = await insertEntry(name, email, phone);

    updateStats(newCount);
    bumpCounter();

    document.getElementById('form-area').style.display   = 'none';
    document.getElementById('success-area').style.display = 'block';
    document.getElementById('position-text').textContent  = 'Sua posição: #' + fmt(newCount);

    // Contagem regressiva → WhatsApp
    var secs    = 3;
    var countEl = document.getElementById('redirect-count');
    countEl.textContent = secs;
    var timer = setInterval(function() {
      secs--;
      countEl.textContent = secs;
      if (secs <= 0) { clearInterval(timer); window.location.href = WA_URL; }
    }, 1000);
  }

  // ── Enter key ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  document.addEventListener('keydown', function(e) {
    if (e.key === 'Enter' && document.getElementById('form-area').style.display !== 'none') {
      handleSubmit();
    }
  });

  // ── Init: carrega contagem atual ao abrir a página ────────────────────────
  getCount().then(function(n) { updateStats(n); });
</script>

<!--
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  COMO CONFIGURAR O CONTADOR REAL (Supabase — grátis, 3 minutos)
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  1. Acesse https://supabase.com e crie uma conta gratuita
  2. Crie um novo projeto
  3. No menu lateral, vá em "SQL Editor" e execute:

       CREATE TABLE waitlist (
         id         bigserial PRIMARY KEY,
         name       text NOT NULL,
         email      text NOT NULL,
         phone      text,
         created_at timestamptz DEFAULT now()
       );

       ALTER TABLE waitlist ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;

       CREATE POLICY "insert_public" ON waitlist
         FOR INSERT WITH CHECK (true);

       CREATE POLICY "count_public" ON waitlist
         FOR SELECT USING (true);

  4. Vá em Settings → API e copie:
       - Project URL  → cole em SUPABASE_URL
       - anon key     → cole em SUPABASE_ANON_KEY

  5. Faça upload do arquivo no GitHub — pronto!
     O contador agora é compartilhado entre TODOS os visitantes em tempo real.

  Sem Supabase? O sistema usa localStorage como fallback (contador por dispositivo).
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
-->

</body>
</html>
